data.description: PRICE ADJUSTMENT!! Perfect 3 bedroom 2 bath 2 car garage home located on a large corner lot in a desirable neighborhood in Temple Terrace. This home offers an open floor plan with almost 1900 sq ft of living area with a spacious living room and dining room combo that is a perfect place to entertain. The kitchen has ample storage space and equipped with newer Stainless Steel Appliances plus an extended breakfast bar ideal for guest or just getting a quick bite. The master bedroom is huge with an area for a home office or nursery. It also includes a Walk-in closet and a master suite featuring double vanity. The second and third bedroom are a nice size with a beautiful, upgraded guest bathroom with a walk in shower. This home is well maintained with a 1 year old roof, 3 year old water heater, and all appliances. You'll love the completely fenced in backyard with plenty of privacy and space to enjoy a nice fire during the cooler months. You'll have enough room to bring your boat, jet ski or rv and a bonus there is NO HOA OR CDD in this neighborhood. You are centrally located to USF main campus, Downtown Tampa, Tampa airport and all of our Gorgeous Florida beaches. There is plenty to do with a ton of Restaurants, Shopping and amusements parks to entertain the whole family. Hurry and make your appointment before this one is long gone!
